  <name>Syltr</name>
  <summary>All-in-one messaging client for KDE Plasma</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Syltr groups the web interfaces of common messaging services (WhatsApp Web,
      Telegram, Slack, Discord, Messenger, and user-defined services) into a single
      window with per-service session isolation, native notifications, and tight
      integration with KDE Plasma.
    </p>
  </description>
